data.title: Swift Go participant banks
data.text:
Join the low-value payment revolution

We’re transforming low-value international payments, forever. Over 630+ banks have already signed up – explore our growing community today.

The following list represents customers that have provided permission to publish their names and are in various stages of implementing the service.

To find out which of these institutions are ready to exchange Swift Go transactions, please consult the GPI directory (downloadable here). If you do not have access to the directory, please contact your Swift account manager or Swift Support.
